<item>
            <title>[HBASE-12386] Replication gets stuck following a transient zookeeper error to remote peer cluster</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12386</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Following a transient ZK error replication gets stuck and remote peers are never updated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Source region servers are reporting continuously the following error in logs:&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;No replication sinks are available&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
